{"tid":2455664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科興：年長群組不良反應比率低　與成年群組相若","createTime":"2021-03-21T09:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T10:02:20.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41980b8df724902ede8aca08b8cb8fd51f4fc919","tid":2455664,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"北京科興品牌與公共關係總監劉沛誠說，從內地一二期年長群組臨床接種情況，以及境外大規模接種情況來看，年長群組接種疫苗出現不良反應比例較低，與成年群組類似，至今並無監測到與疫苗相關的異常情況。 <br />\n<br />\n他在北京的聯防聯控記者會又說，科興滅活疫苗自去年12月以來，已陸續在中國、智利、巴西及土耳其等近30個國家獲批使用，包括緊急使用、有條件上市或正式上市，並且陸續啟動大規模接種工作，在全球已經累積接種7千萬劑。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2383950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2383950&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=33271d7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2383950</a>"},{"pid":"0ccfa704628a871990f292aeb9597ca1af95f922","tid":2455664,"uid":271250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"死咗唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8bc28859dca1caa20880b6f9f6628b0a22b2a1","tid":2455664,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgA5PZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgA5PZE.gif&h=f61db0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzVagEE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzVagEE.gif&h=d1882907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MW45x0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MW45x0.gif&h=79841e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJ9uxc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJ9uxc0.jpg&h=472a0c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbZeJjH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t